lyrics:
[verse]
Huzeyfe Akhan, a name we all know
With talent and charm that truly does show
One look from his eyes, you'll feel at ease
A star shining bright, with a heart that’s at peace

[chorus]
Oh, Huzeyfe Akhan, a leader so grand
Guiding us forward, with a helping hand
He inspires us all, with love and with grace
A shining example, in this vast human race
